item.title: CVE-2019-5462|2024-08-04T19:54:53.486Z -- gitlab -- gitlab%20community%20edition%20and%20gitlab%20enterprise%20edition
item.description: A privilege escalation issue was discovered in GitLab CE/EE 9.0 and later when trigger tokens are not rotated once ownership of them has changed.
